            major airlines and travel providers in Europe and Asia through his
            role as a machine learning engineer, research infrastructure
            manager, and software engineer at Deepair. He developed software
            tools and frameworks that are used by in-house data science teams
            and researchers at esteemed institutions such as the University of
            Illinois at Urbana Champaign, Imperial College London, and the
            University of Notre Dame. He was a part of the team that achieved
            New Distribution Capability (NDC) level 4 certification by the
            International Air Transport Association (IATA).
          </p>

